	/// Returns net signed amount from FY Start Date through As Of Date, while removing fiscal period filters so the sum spans multiple periods. Represents “fiscal YTD expense as-of yesterday” in the selected fiscal year.
	measure 'ER - Expense (FYTD AsOf)' = ```
			
			VAR FY = [ER - Selected Fiscal Year]
			VAR StartDate = [ER - FY Start Date]
			VAR EndDate = [ER - As Of Date]
			RETURN
			    CALCULATE (
			        [ER - Amount (Signed)],
			        REMOVEFILTERS ( 'Dim_Date'[FiscalPeriodNum] ),
			        DATESBETWEEN ( 'Dim_Date'[Date], StartDate, EndDate ),
			        'Dim_Date'[FiscalYear] = FY
			    )
			
			```
